# To-Do App

## Description
A simple, interactive To-Do application to help users manage daily tasks efficiently. Users can add new tasks, mark tasks as complete, and delete tasks. Built with fundamental web technologies: HTML for structure, CSS for styling, and JavaScript for interactivity.

## Features
- **Add New Tasks**: Quickly add to-do items to your list.
- **Mark as Complete**: Toggle tasks as complete or incomplete.
- **Delete Tasks**: Remove tasks from the list.
- **Responsive Design**: Works well on desktop and mobile devices.

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6+)

